	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The word &amp;quot;dear&amp;quot; (महंगा) appropriately fits the context of selling items at a high price. It directly contrasts with &amp;quot;cheap&amp;quot; and implies charging a lot for the items after purchasing them inexpensively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
